sequenceDiagram
    participant Server
    participant Filebeat as "Filebeat Agent"
    participant Logstash as "Logstash"
    participant ES as "Elasticsearch"
    participant KB as "Kibana"
    actor Analyst

    Server-&gt;Filebeat: 1. Write log (e.g., auth failed)
    Filebeat-&gt;Logstash: 2. Forward log
    Logstash-&gt;Logstash: 3. Parse &amp; enrich
    Logstash-&gt;ES: 4. Index document
    Analyst-&gt;KB: 5. Query / view dashboards
    KB-&gt;ES: 6. Query data
    ES--&gt;KB: 7. Return results
    KB--&gt;Analyst: 8. Display alerts &amp; visualizations
